Class RampMeterImpl

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.BaseObjectImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.ControllerIoImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.DeviceImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.RampMeterImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SonarObject, ControllerIO, Device, RampMeter, Storable
public class RampMeterImpl extends DeviceImpl implements RampMeter
A ramp meter is a traffic signal which meters the flow of traffic on a freeway entrance ramp.
Author:
Douglas Lau
